beer.beer_description: Crack open the window to a tastebud paradise of blue skies and salty sea breezes, where the word drinkableness exists. Yes. Say it out loud. Drinkableness. Our Balter Lager greets you with a casual citrus wave, subtle spicy grin and gentle malt hug. A happy place for your mouth. Full of drinkableness.
